These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, eggplant, blueberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, argentine
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, trike
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the german is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person eating broccoli is between the owner of the ferret and the person eating eggplant##2
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | hot-chocolate      | juice      |
| Food          | eggplant   | broccoli   | blueberry       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | mystery | thriller    |
| Nationality   | argentine  | colombian    | german    |
| Pet           | rabbit    | pony    | ferret |
| Transport     | tram  | trike     | motorbike        |

