.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: corn, lettuce, pear
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, romance, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: british, canadian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: bird, snake, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, skateboarding, lacrosse
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person eating pear is between the chinese and the person drinking almond-milk##2
7. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching sports movies and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | water     | soy-milk        | almond-milk      |
| Food          | lettuce    | pear       | corn  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | romance | satire    |
| Nationality   | chinese | british   | canadian    |
| Pet           | snake      | bird  | frog      |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | skateboarding      | baseball |

