The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, singing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, indie, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, subway
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the nigerian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
2. the turkish is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the argentine is the argentine##1
4. the owner of the pony is the fan of indie##1
5. the turkish is on the left of the fan of country##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating mango##2
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
9. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | mango  | eggplant    | pomegranate   |
| Hobby         | card-games | singing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | indie    | country |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | turkish  | argentine  |
| Pet           | hamster     | pony   | hedgehog       |
| Transport     | ship | skateboard     | subway       |

