There 3 different types of food: soy-milkmelon, peas, apricot
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, british, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, basketball
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, boat, tram
1. the person eating peas is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the tram is the russian##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the turkish is on the right of the british##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person eating apricot and the person driving the boat##2
9. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | sprite      | soy-milk     | milk      |
| Food          | apricot     | soy-milkmelon     | peas     |
| Hobby         | fishing      | writing | hiking    |
| Nationality   | russian  | british | turkish     |
| Sport         | swimming   | lacrosse      | basketball |
| Transport     | tram | train      | boat          |

