2. the owner of the mouse is the person eating avocado##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
4. the colombian is on the far right##1
5. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the cat##1
6. the nurse is between the person eating broccoli and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating mango##1
8. the writer is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |      2       |       3       |
| Food          | mango           | avocado       | broccoli       |
| Job           | pilot | nurse    | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | thriller | horror        |
| Music-Genre   | trance          | techno        | dubstep       |
| Nationality   | mexican        | indonesian     | colombian      |
| Pet           | rabbit           | mouse   | cat           |

