.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, scientific, family
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, r&b, trance
3 different pets are kept: goat, dog, cat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, cycling, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, bike, quad-bike
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the owner of the cat##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of metal##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | tea     | sprite   | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | family  | musical  |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | r&b  | trance        |
| Pet           | cat       | dog   | goat |
| Sport         | cycling      | cricket | surfing   |
| Transport     | bike   | quad-bike     | train |

 